Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with the phrase "eighth-grader syndrome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are most prone to it around the end of the eighth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an adorable, yet dreadful disease resulting from new-found self-awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mixing with an overly active imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that results in the peculiar behavior we're all quite painfully familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the guy who only read weekly manga mags up until yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then suddenly starts reading the \Noriginal English versions of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or someone who has absolutely no idea what coffee tastes like,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but still tries to develop a taste for drinking it black.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's those who believe that they possess special powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become obsessed with the occult stuff overnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During his junior high days,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this boy was a textbook example of eighth-grader syndrome too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He named himself the Dark Flame \NMaster, and his catchphrase was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Vanish into the embrace of dark flames!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so, so, so, so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna forget it! I wanna forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merely remembering this embarrassing condition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes one want to disappear from the surface of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,Do you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Normal, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw it all out later, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you bought this one with the \Nmoney you got from New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you just leave it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you declaring you would rule the world with this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to wear that weird coat a lot back then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! If I can live without remembering that, so can you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, it's Yuuta's entrance ceremony today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parents don't usually attend high school entrance ceremonies anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Judging from her uniform, she goes to the same high school as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's her! That girl from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I got on a later train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I intentionally chose a different high school to everyone else from my junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first impression is the most important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be over-conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just blend in smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Togashi Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never loose this cursed bandage from my arm, and for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing so would unleash the Black Flame Dragon on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That memory pains my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been on my own in that class ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Don't worry about the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here knows me from back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perish, enveloped in the flames of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contained and sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you spare me some pencil lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which junior high are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's no one else from my old school here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hardly know anyone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Isshiki Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Togashi Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, yeah! Just play it straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hooray for my high school debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how do you like the girls in this class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice collection of hotties, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sweet, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's in my class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Aiming high, aren't you? Nibutani, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nibutani Shinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's easily in first place on my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye... My eye is reacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I crossed the pits of Hell to meet you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, she just confessed to you! I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're getting it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's... Yeah, I'm sure she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's... She's got eighth-grader syndrome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye... My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bottom shelf... The bottom shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse had to go somewhere, so I was told to give you these eyedrops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up or we'll be late for the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one on my balcony last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reacted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, our paths once crossed, \Nmeasureless eons before this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I saw you, my Wicked Eye revealed to me our destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I sought the chance to meet you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bitter taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doubtlessly, this is the work of the Cult of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must seal this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I need any more proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Eye wields darkness tamed by the power of a pure heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it itself is defiled by darkness, it cannot endure anything pure, such as holy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely eighth-grader syndrome. She's a textbook case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We almost fell victim to the enemy's schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be more careful from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be enveloped by the flames of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Wicked Eye is perfectly clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about level 7 warlocks and their powe—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entirety of the future and the past is but an open book before—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked where you heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see! Yuuta, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was at the gym earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought no one was listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a word to anyone about this, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The principles of the Deep Horizon and the composition changes in—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No "Dark Flame Master"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No "wielder of the flames of darkness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! I decided to leave all that behind me when I graduated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single tiny little bit of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're now a level 8 warlock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about eighth-grader syndrome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the Dark Flame Master or any kind of warlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal high school freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you look less shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a secret: you're an \Naverage high school freshman too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my Wicked Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it even exists in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see my eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it... No way. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment. I'll put it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a colored contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I can feel it... inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An afterimage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one more time: I left that crap behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't come anywhere near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And shut up about the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've seen my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract between us is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We share the heart of darkness. We are spiritual soulmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}so{\i0} deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead. You should hurry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the freshman address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshman representative, Nibutani Shinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that weirdo latched onto me like that, there must still be something off about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This beautiful spring day with all the cherry trees in full blossom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}is the day we join the community of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Representing all freshmen, I would like to give words of gratitude for this grand ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the freshman representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're done with the \Nintroductions, let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be sure to check your schedule when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got some time after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few of us were talking about going for lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... inviting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is it Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl you took to the nurse's earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you promise her you'd walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want nothing to do with her! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You don't swing that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want weird rumors to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki, you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's lost her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just moved here, so she doesn't know the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you walk her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you live very close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live on the floor above me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry! I'll come next time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when did you move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the only person up there was some office lady living on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed residences the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi Tooka is my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you moved in with your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that's what we lead others to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's actually a powerful sorceress who oversees the Deep Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she awakens her powers, I'm no match for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I use my Wicked Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary can she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not, Rikka! Victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised she gets mad at you with all the nonsense you keep going on about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of the Dark Flame Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could break through the Overseers' barrier and find the Deep Horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come up with a new attack for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing roller shoes? Are you five or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have superior mobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I'm wearing these and the enemy attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke a few of my ribs... But it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! We're in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you like? My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up! Up! Down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.63,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takanashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left! Right! Left! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.19,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The train...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Insert the coin now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now B, A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "B, A"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mana potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Overseers are pulling the strings from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train already left, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you accept my powers now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. You looked pretty surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, B and A stand for banana and apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It differs by the season, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop wasting my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They meant to deliver these to Ms. Takanashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she wasn't at home, so they \Nasked me to take care of it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they call themselves movers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned home late due to the Overseers' interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been home by three according to pl—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takanashi's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have so much stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too much for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all precious treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's all junk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and get dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many useful items here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's spring-loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be used as a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gungnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when defending...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your stuff with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, another Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as pretty as your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, what happened to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Eye harnesses darkness using sacred powe—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare us the backstory, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumeha, don't take that out around h— Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you slung that over your back, it'd be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta did that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wore a black coat, had that on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly had some strange ideas back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always chanting spells or whatever those were before meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, isn't it time you left for your night shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them it was trash, and they just go rummaging through it anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the life of the Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I left that all behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. Not even slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff's all totally pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as the Flames of \NDarkness or the Power of the Dark Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The power is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish into the embrace of dark flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought they'd be too valuable to just throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some money by putting them up for auction instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold if you stand out here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}spring was actually quite warm this year.
