Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:32.16,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}dare ga nanto iou to tadashisa nante wakannai ze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:34.88,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}futsuu ni nagareteku nichijou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.35,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}muri shite najimase to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.29,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}shizunjimatta kouseitachi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.48,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}kande nonde haite ware
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:46.99,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}konna boku wo wakatte hoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:52.30,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}iitai kedo ienakute
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.33,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}nande daremo wakatte kunnai no to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.44,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}omou no wa zeitaku nano kana nano kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:07.58,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}kanjouteki na taiyou wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.86,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}netsu wo agesugite dounika narisou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:17.93,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}sakebitakute shou ga nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:24.27,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}gamushara ni mo tometeru identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:26.58,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}inside my identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:29.08,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}inside my justice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:31.72,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}tamashii wa ite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.48,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}{\an8}ibasho wa doko
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:11.69,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Inside identity! Where do I belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:24.53,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Getting it wrong is a shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:27.10,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Being honest hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:32.16,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Whatever people say, they don't know what's right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:34.88,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The boring river of time flows on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.35,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}When the stars tried to fit in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.29,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}They ended up sinking into it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.48,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}So chew them, swallow them, and spit them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:46.99,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}"I wish you understood me"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:52.30,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}That's what I want to say, but I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.33,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}"No one ever understands me"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.44,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Is it selfish to think that? Is it? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:07.58,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The emotional Sun in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.86,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Overheated, reaching its limit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:17.93,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Of course I want to shout
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:24.27,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}My fast and furious identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:26.58,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Inside my identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:29.08,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Inside my justice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:31.72,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}There's a soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.48,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}But where do I belong?
